name: Yam yam
summary:
Yam! Yam!? was produced by Dooyong in 1990. 
 
Dooyong released 11 different machines in our database under this trade name, starting in 1990. 
 
Other machines made by Dooyong during the time period Yam! Yam!? was produced include Wise Guy, Last Day, The, Gun Dealer, Pollux, and Gulf Storm.
